### Steps to reproduce
```
this.$router.options // should be the options that user passed to vue-rotuer
```

## Solution

I think we should change 

```ts
declare module 'vue/types/vue' {
  interface Vue {
    $router: VueRouter
    $route: Route
  }
}
```
to 


```ts
import { RouterOptions } from './router'

declare module 'vue/types/vue' {
  interface Vue {
    $router: VueRouter & { options: RouterOptions }
    $route: Route
  }
}
```

